{"tid":2439883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[何謂左膠]深層次討論左膠問題","createTime":"2021-03-09T14:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T07:46:08.000Z","uid":130385,"like":16,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e6712cc042fdf693afb7839766764ac9e6fbb381","tid":2439883,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"左膠之所以係膠  唔需要我點詳細解釋 好多人都明白  就係嚴以待己 寬以律人<br />\n佢地既理想都係同現實脫節 好多時都不問是非黑白  <br />\n但其實左膠有好多種,背後亦代表住不同的勢力<br />\n <br />\n第一種左膠是只看是但合乎其信仰   在他們的世界觀中只有權利 沒有責任 例子是BLM 女權等  同時佢地亦欺善怕惡 而且大多數的所謂平權都係同性慾有關 同性戀  幻幻  又或是激起矛盾的問題 黑人 難民問題之類<br />\n   依班人主要係屬於第一類 programmed idiot,佢地的人數亦係最多<br />\n佢地係係長期被傳媒洗腦的, 今天西方傳媒界都比某一部份既人買起哂<br />\n變左做產業鏈的一部份, 睇bbc cnn 點反trump就知.<br />\n只要CNN叫佢反  佢就會反 無獨立思考 怕埋唔到堆 環保左膠應該算第一類  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0oQVqJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0oQVqJ.png&h=2f5dbe8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHzpfqJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHzpfqJ.png&h=96e10ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbJaaY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbJaaY3.png&h=a4d2681a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pCytG8o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpCytG8o.png&h=d557a4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdSaVto.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdSaVto.png&h=72b24e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二種左膠係收錢辦事者 性質同五毛類似 佢地唔信左膠思想,只係有人比錢叫佢地帶風向<br />\n制造仇恨或搬弄是非之類, 同時亦會進行暴力行動 好似BLM之類<br />\n風向帶完後 自然會有政客甚至法官行動 完成佢地既目的<br />\n睇TRUMP當時發生咩事就知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOzgQZf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOzgQZf.png&h=7dab1dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3brtMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3brtMw.png&h=dd3793ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vgrtMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vgrtMw.png&h=26d37293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8ONddb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8ONddb.png&h=41a6f7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前2者都係NEW WORLD ORDER的一部份, 目的係建立世界政府, 統治地球<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再有一班左膠 係共產主意者, 想透過破壞現有世界建立的規則, 實現共產或社會主義<br />\n依班人有部份係社會的失敗者 亦有部份係長期被蘇聯同中國浸透的左翼教師洗腦出黎<br />\n依班友只係用黎制造混亂的 useful idiot NWO完成之後就係要清除的主要敵人<br />\n左膠的武器是道德高地同言論自由, 世界統治完成後用槍就可以直接對付他們了<br />\n<br />\n所以左膠的勢力應該是最少有2類, NWO 和共產主義者"},{"pid":"32eef7e8d775ffec00a5f92714444af2254b9c23","tid":2439883,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩card game黎咁正嘅"},{"pid":"d5fc1e9e101abe6e5e32c0a2fe9f1335a3d9c4e8","tid":2439883,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32eef7e8d775ffec00a5f92714444af2254b9c23","tid":2439883,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩card game黎咁正嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"光明會卡   我有全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b015b1585b7b3afce24fc63c525f69cd50bd4cd","tid":2439883,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185f56c9d4ee76240fb1483e251447dba81aff85","tid":2439883,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"共產主義對世界嘅威脅從來都冇消失過"},{"pid":"2edfcd241dac33ed04d3cfb4b5b2df43fb8854df","tid":2439883,"uid":182222,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-0