mal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好將全部左膠歸納埋一齊<br />\n有d左膠要共產   有d左膠只係要性 or特權  唔想比人共產<br />\n有d左膠單純係關心動物+環保  狗重要過人 <br />\n分享人地d野可以   分享自己果時就變左右派  依d左膠又係另一派<br />\n左膠世界係好複雜  勢力好多好唔同<br />\n只係勢力人士為左權力同利益用傳媒將佢地講成係同一類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24cf4dc0d5ccc5dbe522be5a492be166eea61b7","tid":2439883,"uid":96439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1e9e8cfeca4d9903fbda27c37e2cda4be987af00","tid":2439883,"uid":87765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93d1ea48f69bc94df8f9cb56e6e9e2490b6dc3c1","tid":2439883,"uid":96439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08e884a78f2d1810eaedf2b48e121f80fb168259","tid":2439883,"uid":130385,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"同人討論   唔係教學  依d只係拋磚引玉 <br />\n你有乜高見呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔係左膠挑機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"討論左右派 但係經濟上唔講Milton Friedman , Hayes 同Keynes <br />\n咁仲有咩討論層次可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"不過我地依家口中嘅左膠應該主要係political left而未必係economic left?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"我認為係現代已經冇得再分開politics同macro-economy<br />\n<br />\n事實上要睇學者屌左膠都未必係睇哲學、political economy書，反而係睇環保議題、動保、女權、黑人呢啲大issue <br />\n<br />\n據我觀察，左膠普遍問題係排斥incremental change，盲目追求evolutionary change；另外就係如Peter singer所講，唔肯承認即使人係自私，但仍然會有契機合作而socially good(the Darwinian left)。"},{"pid":"5e8a6b959e450fc404458c810a27dd4e5b5ec69f","tid":2439883,"uid":15830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"060a08f76dbdec9cff6ff0564e86f709e5bba70b","tid":2439883,"uid":77180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2edfcd241dac33ed04d3cfb4b5b2df43fb8854df","tid"